    <entry>
      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/17/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/17/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://qk.it-02.cf">my blog</a>!<br />I’m glad to have this opportunity to introduce myself.<br />​</p><h1 id="quick-start"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#quick-start"></a> Quick Start</h1><p>First, my name is <strong>qingkong</strong>, a 15 boy study at Xx snior high school in <strong>China</strong>.</p><p>​</p><h2 id="personality"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#personality"></a> Personality</h2><p>In my opinion, I’m open minded, easy-going,warm hearted with sunshine smile.<br />​<br />​</p><h2 id="hobby"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#hobby"></a> Hobby</h2><p>There are plenty of things,but my favorite is still this. I often spend my spare time on <strong>learning computer technology</strong>, especially programming. I think it’s an excellent way to improve myself.</p><h3 id="a-little-bit-of-achievement-about-programming"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#a-little-bit-of-achievement-about-programming"></a> A little bit of achievement about programming</h3><ol><li>A homepage that I wrote in php<br /><img src="/photo/a.jpeg" alt="" /></li><li>this blog</li></ol><p>​&gt;Others have disappeared into time</p><h2 id="dream"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#dream"></a> Dream</h2><p>My dream is to get into a good university and become a network worker. That way I can continue to do what I love to do. Hopefully, my dreams come true.Thank you very much for reading!</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> self-introduce </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Python三元表达式</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/11/Python%E4%B8%89%E5%85%83%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/11/Python%E4%B8%89%E5%85%83%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="python-三元表达式假吗"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#python-三元表达式假吗"></a> Python 三元表达式假吗</h1><p>在我查阅相关资料后,发现并不存在这一说法(这表达式真的太假了)。<br />那难道我就是想水个文章吗？当然不可能,我从不(确信)水文章。<br />Python是不存在三元表达式一说,但却存在着与三元表达式有着异曲同工之妙的<strong>条件表达式</strong><br />它的结构如下：</p><blockquote><p>表达式（1）为 True 执行语句 if 条件表达式（1） else 表达式（1）为 False 执行语句</p></blockquote><p>当你看完之后,是不是觉得有手就行<br />是吧,我也觉得。<br />既然都知道这玩意是怎么一回事了,那我们就直接开搞。</p><h1 id="学费了但是该怎么用捏"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#学费了但是该怎么用捏"></a> 学费了,但是该怎么用捏</h1><p>剧透：用法也是有手就行(我奶奶都会用)</p><h2 id="让if语句活得更轻松"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#让if语句活得更轻松"></a> 让if语句活得更轻松</h2><p>让if语句活得更轻松？怎么个轻松法呢？<br />让我们直接上实例</p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 原语句</span></span><br><span class="line">age = <span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> age &gt;= <span class="number">18</span> :</span><br><span class="line">    cn = <span class="string">&quot;成年&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    cn = <span class="string">&quot;未成年&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 条件表达式处理后</span></span><br><span class="line">age = <span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line">cn = <span class="string">&quot;成年&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> age &gt;= <span class="number">18</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="string">&quot;未成年&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(cn)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>条件表达式处理后是不是轻松爆了。</p><h2 id="给函数减负"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#给函数减负"></a> 给函数减负</h2><p>有些简单的判定逻辑,可以直接使用条件表达式简化,例如判断传入参数是否为偶数。</p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">even_num</span>(<span class="params">num</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">True</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> num % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="literal">False</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="用于列表推导式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#用于列表推导式"></a> 用于列表推导式</h2><p>在列表推导式知识点中,也存在条件表达式的落地应用,例如下述代码。</p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">9</span>, <span class="number">10</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ret = [i for i in li if i % 2 == 0]</span></span><br><span class="line">ret = [i <span class="keyword">if</span> i % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="literal">None</span> <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> li]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(ret)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="和匿名函数交朋友"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#和匿名函数交朋友"></a> 和匿名函数交朋友</h2><p>有时候可以将列表表达式与 lambda 进行结合,让代码变得更加简洁。</p><blockquote><p>声明一个函数，返回较大值</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">max</span>(<span class="params">a, b</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> a &gt; b:</span><br><span class="line">        ret = a</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        ret = b</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> ret</span><br><span class="line">r = <span class="built_in">max</span>(<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>由于上述代码非常简单,可以直接使用 lambda 匿名函数实现。</p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">max</span> = <span class="keyword">lambda</span> a, b: a <span class="keyword">if</span> a &gt; b <span class="keyword">else</span> b</span><br><span class="line">r = <span class="built_in">max</span>(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(r)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="提高场景"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#提高场景"></a> 提高场景</h2><p>Python 条件表达式可以嵌套使用,但是建议最多嵌套两层,而且是在代码简单的情况下,具体编码如下所示,你需要重点学习下述问题。</p><blockquote><p>在嵌套的时候,还需要注意 if 和 else 配对问题。</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 编写一个条件表达式，首先判断其值大于20，然后在判断是奇数（案例，无实际意义）</span></span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="number">19</span></span><br><span class="line">ret = <span class="string">&quot;小于20&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> num &lt; <span class="number">20</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> (<span class="string">&quot;奇数&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> num % <span class="number">2</span> == <span class="number">1</span> <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="string">&quot;偶数&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(ret)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="扩展知识"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#扩展知识"></a> 扩展知识</h2><p>在很多地方会将 Python 的条件表达式进行扩展，出现下述两种用法，但都属于炫技能力，实战性不强。</p><p>例如下述内容：</p><h3 id="元组条件表达式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#元组条件表达式"></a> 元组条件表达式</h3><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">age = <span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line">cn = (<span class="string">&quot;未成年&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;成年&quot;</span>)[age &gt;= <span class="number">18</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(cn)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>语法格式如下所示</p><blockquote><p>(当后面的表达式为假时返回,当后面的表达式为真时返回)[条件表达式]</p></blockquote><h3 id="字典条件表达式"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#字典条件表达式"></a> 字典条件表达式</h3><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">age = <span class="number">20</span></span><br><span class="line">cn = &#123;<span class="literal">False</span>: <span class="string">&quot;未成年&quot;</span>, <span class="literal">True</span>: <span class="string">&quot;成年&quot;</span>&#125;[age &gt;= <span class="number">18</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(cn)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>你会发现，上述两种写法都有一些故弄玄虚，而且代码 非常不易 阅读，所以不建议实战编码时使用。</p>]]></content>
      
      
